Hi <redacted>,

Delivering voice automation for a single client is an achievement. The real challenge, however, lies in delivering it repeatedly across multiple clients, maintaining quality and efficiency without creating chaos. This is where a systematic approach becomes essential.

Scaling your voice automation services requires standardization. Think of it as a playbook: a clear template, an effective onboarding checklist, consistent outcomes, and robust reporting. This framework ensures predictable, high-quality results every time.

Our Whitelabel solution is built precisely for this model. It empowers you to deliver Awaz.ai's powerful voice automation under your own brand, with dedicated client workspaces. This allows you to manage each client's needs separately while leveraging a unified, repeatable delivery system.
Your Practical Packaging Approach:

    Define one flagship workflow you can deliver consistently to most clients.
    Create a baseline AI agent template, only customizing what is absolutely client-specific.
    Use consistent call outcomes for streamlined performance measurement and reporting.
    Sync these outcomes into CRM or Google Sheets with API for clean follow-ups and comprehensive client reporting.

To help you master this, our CEO is hosting a free 60-minute Whitelabel webinar. This session will cover key features of the Awaz.ai Whitelabel platform and provide valuable insights into implementing a scalable service delivery model.

Register for the Whitelabel Webinar:
hxxps://sendy[.]digitalinfluencers[.]co/l/lQl3wjaAZqaZD763eA8Rzc6Q/ZTe8tKq3uq0ZWr6PE9OE2Q/zpPSdYUvxOmoSlR3OBHvOA

We look forward to helping you expand your service offerings with confidence.


